"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"金色财经报道，今日在美国国会的加密听证会上，众议员Rashida Tlaib询问了[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)的能源使用情况，指出[加密货币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)行业“目前消耗的能源足以为一个小国提供动力”。Tlaib说，[比特币挖矿](https://www.bitcoin86.com/wk/)消耗的能源比阿根廷、苹果、Facebook和微软加起来还要多。对此，Stellar首席执行官Denelle Dixon指出，加密货币有不同类型的共识机制，它们使用更少的能源或可能更环保。Dixon指出了Marathon Digital在蒙大拿州的发电厂和Greenidge Generation的纽约矿场都是曾经关闭的燃煤发电厂被重新用于加密用途的例子。Dixon说：“我们都需要把精力集中在减少能源使用上。”\",\"timestamp\":1639132279,\"title\":\"Stellar首席执行官：加密货币有不同类型的共识机制，有些更环保\"},\"digest\":\"ZwxRzHGOvdxgSqY0UpM8xxNtuCrwdxjiUvXDkuRRyNg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xBb33c18F0117BE518f68f391241296A81bD52dA8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5mX4iKO9xW4Vdrwmv3NtePRDhWn2UmyEc2oB510CvhE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"I8djSq69NgzHyHZ6-a1hHeKZDwEwLQhg1XU4Wd33Bk8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"xcZ6Tn3Bme-TJBVALfyI1_rSMVEZRPsZ9fT9q9iex5Lp2UWae0ZJZskwOLPm1WJNA5pgO5SY886nCsPfJhIPUQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x26254796fd24fa1e3d403b2aed777d404f82aa1eb244a0e37d4081fb2719fea964682019e19fcfeb4cea59aacb5e0838cb2a6e1d78d81519ff289a7858b2f8241b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"5mX4iKO9xW4Vdrwmv3NtePRDhWn2UmyEc2oB510CvhE\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"I8djSq69NgzHyHZ6-a1hHeKZDwEwLQhg1XU4Wd33Bk8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ZwxRzHGOvdxgSqY0UpM8xxNtuCrwdxjiUvXDkuRRyNg\"}"